{
  "stem": "24409.9",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they did-- I know Paris, and I know in-- in-- I think in Warsaw, too, I think, there is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Berlin there was one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they did it much better than I did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't have a office there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't have a sign there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just had the stamp, and there all of us they gave the stamps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't need all this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in my-- my personality, I asked for the big show.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was much simpler, and it cost less money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in jail in Athens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was to be deported to Germany, to be handed over to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a document where the British Naval agents-- Naval Intelligence-- informs-- no, the-- no, the British ambassador in Athens informs the foreign secretary in London that the US Naval Intelligence informs him that I am already deported from Athens.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was to be deported to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, on the border-- you see, Greece doesn't border Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In between, you have to go through Yugoslav's territory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- when we came to Idomene-- I-D-O-M-E-N-E-- Idomene, which is this small border station between Greece and Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew, now, when I am in Yugoslavia, the next thing is the border, and the Yugoslavs have to get rid of me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't want me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next thing, he says, that they give me, hand me over to the German-- Austrian-- Austrian-- German authorities.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I decided I will not-- I decided before, I will not fall into Eichmann's hands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eichmann had threatened me, you know that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once, in Bucharest, I called our office.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
